@{
    Layout = null; // Kita tidak mahu sidebar muncul semasa maintenance
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>Sistem Sedang Dikemaskini - KenalPhishing</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script type="module" src="https://unpkg.com/ionicons@7.1.0/dist/ionicons/ionicons.esm.js"></script>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif;
        }

        .maintenance-card {
            max-width: 500px;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        .icon-box {
            font-size: 80px;
            color: #ffc107;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #1a1a2e;
        }

        p {
            color: #6c757d;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="maintenance-card">
        <div class="icon-box">
            <ion-icon name="construct-outline"></ion-icon>
        </div>
        <h1>Mod Penyelenggaraan</h1>
        <p class="mt-3">
            Mohon maaf, sistem <strong>KenalPhishing</strong> sedang menjalani proses kemas kini berjadual untuk meningkatkan tahap keselamatan anda.
        </p>
        <p class="small text-muted">
            Sila cuba sebentar lagi. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda.
        </p>
        <hr class="my-4 opacity-25">
        <a href="@Url.Action("Index", "Home")" class="btn btn-dark rounded-pill px-4">Kembali ke Laman Utama</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>